22148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T05:03:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大學邊間讀咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔識睇字？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4051155448a915d43fe285cf65337bb625292d2","tid":5732,"uid":22148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T05:04:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做內部MT?<br />\n係唔係好悶？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好challenging.. 乜部門都要stay.. <br />\n<br />\n升得快，但亦快被勸退.."},{"pid":"8b98219e878d38a95e4f4002b9047e2dee344ad6","tid":5732,"uid":22148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T05:06:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>宏x個mt係咪伏</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上公司官網check check.. 如果講明有rotation, d function and skill set 係比較實在，就應該無乜伏..<br />\n<br />\nM記呢幾年做得一般，可能間公司太守舊.."},{"pid":"02a949e280fa6e0b835c242d235720eeff2764b3","tid":5732,"uid":22148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T05:09:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>畢業之後，做咗幾年嘢，都係喺保險公司工作..<br />\n做過GI, Life, Broker firm, 就係未做過Agent。接觸嘅工作範圍包括：Claim, UW, BD, Brokerage, AD, Distribution, IT, FP&amp;amp;amp;A, Strategy, MIS..<br />\n<br />\n你哋問，我盡量答啦...<br />\n<br />\n利申：唔係Agent，無135牌</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有咩係抵買，邊d搵笨</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你係問公司 定 產品先？<br />\n<br />\n公司就無乜大分別.. <br />\n<br />\n產品的話，就唔好揀d供勁多年的，有錢咪lump sum 放落d high saving.. 有d plan offer 3-4% rate, 仲好過定期 ibond"},{"pid":"e938ad524811cf38a10375005ea7e0cc2d2c32cf","tid":5732,"uid":998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T05:18:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>畢業之後，做咗幾年嘢，都係喺保險公司工作..<br />\n做過GI, Life, Broker firm, 就係未做過Agent。接觸嘅工作範圍包括：Claim, UW, BD, Brokerage, AD, Distribution, IT, FP&amp;amp;amp;amp;A, Strategy, MIS..<br />\n<br />\n你哋問，我盡量答啦...<br />\n<br />\n利申：唔係Agent，無135牌</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有咩係抵買，邊d搵笨</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你係問公司 定 產品先？<br />\n<br />\n公司就無乜大分別.. <br />\n<br />\n產品的話，就唔好揀d供勁多年的，有錢咪lump sum 放落d high saving.. 有d plan offer 3-4% rate, 仲好過定期 ibond</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係offer定估計先，成日驚保險plan有古惑所以唔考慮。<br />\n因為老豆老母都中過招，計比你睇果陣就計4%一年十年，到真係次年除翻開一年2%都無"},{"pid":"4d5a604120847960ffb966d1bab6c441dbcb98c3","tid":5732,"uid":998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T05:19:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>畢業之後，做咗幾年嘢，都係喺保險公司工作..<br />\n做過GI, Life, Broker firm, 就係未做過Agent。接觸嘅工作範圍包括：Claim, UW, BD, Brokerage, AD, Distribution, IT, FP&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;A, Strategy, MIS..<br />\n<br />\n你哋問，我盡量答啦...<br />\n<br />\n利申：唔係Agent，無135牌</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有咩係抵買，邊d搵笨</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你係問公司 定 產品先？<br />\n<br />\n公司就無乜大分別.. <br />\n<br />\n產品的話，就唔好揀d供勁多年的，有錢咪lump sum 放落d high saving.. 有d plan offer 3-4% rate, 仲好過定期 ibond</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係offer定估計先，成日驚保險plan有古惑所以唔考慮。<br />\n因為老豆老母都中過招，計比你睇果陣就計4%一年十年，到真係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">攞果</span></strong></span>年除翻開一年2%都無</blockquote>"},{"pid":"2eb248006b92876b8f20caa34af44469ce48f17d","tid":5732,"uid":25213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T05:21:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>畢業之後，做咗幾年嘢，都係喺保險公司工作..<br />\n做過GI, Life, Broker firm, 就係未做過Agent。接觸嘅工作範圍包括：Claim, UW, BD, Brokerage, AD, Distribution, IT, FP&amp;amp;amp;amp;A, Strategy, MIS..<br />\n<br />\n你哋問，我盡量答啦...<br />\n<br />\n利申：唔係Agent，無135牌</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有咩係抵買，邊d搵笨</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你係問公司 定 產品先？<br />\n<br />\n公司就無乜大分別.. <br />\n<br />\n產品的話，就唔好揀d供勁多年的，有錢咪lump sum 放落d high saving.. 有d plan offer 3-4% rate, 仲好過定期 ibond</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nd plan 實際既rate係唔係仲差過強積金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5175c8540fd5f1f4e93255ff5adb8bd177733fcf","tid":5732,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T05:23:09.000Z","msg":"你d agent同事生仔有冇屎忽?"},{"pid":"ffba23edc9a3834eddff0ba203ef43da9c75a97a","tid":5732,"uid":1809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T05:24:31.000Z","msg":"我下個月考paper2 有無內部筆記or notes俾到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1fb9a0f739156f622e501e8aaf64dbde738cf02","tid":5732,"uid":262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T05:25:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大學邊間讀咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔識睇字？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你老味咁你有冇講你讀咩呀傻閪<br />\n唔怪得做保險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3e12eb99e0e2d5d7214f6819c2d9fd16fbe87dd","tid":5732,"uid":22148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T05:30:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>畢業之後，做咗幾年嘢，都係喺保險公司工作..<br />\n做過GI, Life, Broker firm, 就係未做過Agent。接觸嘅工作範圍包括：Claim, UW, BD, Brokerage, AD, Distribution, IT, FP&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;A, Strategy, MIS..<br />\n<br />\n你哋問，我盡量答啦...<br />\n<br />\n利申：唔係Agent，無135牌</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有咩係抵買，邊d搵笨</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你係問公司 定 產品先？<br />\n<br />\n公司就無乜大分別.. <br />\n<br />\n產品的話，就唔好揀d供勁多年的，有錢咪lump sum 放落d high saving.. 有d plan offer 3-4% rate, 仲好過定期 ibond</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係offer定估計先，成日驚保險plan有古惑所以唔考慮。<br />\n因為老豆老母都中過招，計比你睇果陣就計4%一年十年，到真係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">攞果</span></strong></span>年除翻開一年2%都無</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以叫你買年期短嘅，舊時果班買親都係20-30年，全部都係 <span style=\"color: red;\">forecasted rate of return</span> 話你知咩回報，派幾多最終都係由公司決定，加埋長年期會有大變數，大公司派嘅dividend亦會低好多。<br />\n<br />\n近年OCI收緊好多，禁止保險經紀亂吹，會manage返客戶expectation。同時，市場上亦多咗d 保証回報的產品，你可以選擇d有保證回報+短年期嘅產品咪ok!<br />\n<br />\n加埋唔好信曬Agent講，因為好多agent只可以賣一家保險公司product，賣花一定讚花香！"},{"pid":"166d5cdd82e866e54e0c3d430525e26007157eba","tid":5732,"uid":22148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T05:34:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你d agent同事生仔有冇屎忽?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有.. 要呃人，先要呃自己！<br />\n<br />\n喺客戶面前，佢哋都係幫緊人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n喺公司面前，佢哋都係幫公司賺緊錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無精算做pricing，佢哋賣9咩<br />\n無claims，佢哋邊有票post上FB"},{"pid":"e62552f50d4fa9f2144a03aed0ee89114ce3cc28","tid":5732,"uid":22148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T05:36:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>畢業之後，做咗幾年嘢，都係喺保險公司工作..<br />\n做過GI, Life, Broker firm, 就係未做過Agent。接觸嘅工作範圍包括：Claim, UW, BD, Brokerage, AD, Distribution, IT, FP&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;A, Strategy, MIS..<br />\n<br />\n你哋問，我盡量答啦...<br />\n<br />\n利申：唔係Agent，無135牌</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有咩係抵買，邊d搵笨</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你係問公司 定 產品先？<br />\n<br />\n公司就無乜大分別.. <br />\n<br />\n產品的話，就唔好揀d供勁多年的，有錢咪lump sum 放落d high saving.. 有d plan offer 3-4% rate, 仲好過定期 ibond</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nd plan 實際既rate係唔係仲差過強積金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMPF差好多.. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nMPF個Fee逐年收，唔理升跌... 仲收得好甘..."},{"pid":"dba89e603d1aa46e10aa08764350addb7a1c5a4b","tid":5732,"uid":22148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T05:37:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>大學邊間讀咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔識睇字？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你老味咁你有冇講你讀咩呀傻閪<br />\n唔怪得做保險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n毒男科.."},{"pid":"3a6374eb145ebd0e2f71a9a0b330c160d2484f8f","tid":5732,"uid":22148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T05:38:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我下個月考paper2 有無內部筆記or notes俾到我<img src=