嘢同銀行果班批loan好似.. 都係document嘢<br />\n<br />\n日日睇case, e.g. 客戶收入、健康報告、所有影響保費嘢..<br />\nOk咪pass俾上司 approve 出單<br />\n唔ok咪 re-underwrite / 有 UW decision."},{"pid":"65a8b9560fd67323752eb43ac35d681ff5e0c58f","tid":5732,"uid":19970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T06:28:05.000Z","msg":"有冇做過aia 係咪伏"},{"pid":"48c6650c6b9d0f4f0ff98d6f11bf6ebbadeeae68","tid":5732,"uid":5794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T06:29:55.000Z","msg":"Actuarial science?<br />\nAssociate左未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3db3b87cf27506b4c8f600f6acc918865082156","tid":5732,"uid":22148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T06:32:04.000Z","msg":"大家冷靜d.. 唔好俾咁多負評.. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我哋唔係agent, 佢哋都係自己打自己工<br />\n<br />\n其實我哋都好怕d agents.. 佢哋為咗做生意無所不用其極<br />\n<br />\n而家香港得返2-3成係agent數，但佢哋d行為搞垮成個行業 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de9068f2e2cd520f8424aae75e06b80668ca20d7","tid":5732,"uid":22148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T06:32:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇做過aia 係咪伏</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好鬼忙.. 8點後收工是正常的..."},{"pid":"b087c2b8a0ffc5e84e2f3ed1c5f6fa6f25c379ab","tid":5732,"uid":22148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T06:34:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Actuarial science?<br />\nAssociate左未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有讀，但最後無考曬.. 無興趣.."},{"pid":"0ca2b6e723838ff8c68f3adfcf52e0fb0059e355","tid":5732,"uid":5794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T06:36:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇做過aia 係咪伏</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好鬼忙.. 8點後收工是正常的...</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇邊間<br />\nGroup office 係遲開工早收工, lunch有差唔多兩個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過都係睇你邊個departme