><br />\n<br />\n可能職位高d人尊重佢喇<br />\n不過我覺得佢老細好人d"},{"pid":"5616774261ab28c174289d0c9a1c4b0bff95aba9","tid":5732,"uid":22148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T09:24:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2efba4d2012df69577bef7fffd18933b44436789","tid":5732,"uid":28594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T09:50:52.000Z","msg":"final year 報佐AIA 個service &amp;operations 既associate program, 想問下知唔知係做d 咩既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人工同前景如何<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f6193f9c0d317175b18370f6115f90ede415bba","tid":5732,"uid":22148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T00:53:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>final year 報佐AIA 個service &amp;amp;operations 既associate program, 想問下知唔知係做d 咩既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人工同前景如何<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔太熟會做d乜.. 聽名，感覺似做project去streamline/reengineer operation &amp; customer services.<br />\n<br />\n其實aia做得唔錯.. 值得一試.."},{"pid":"7735dca383ddc25cd2890f08d1fe4cbb55df7bf6","tid":5732,"uid":22148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T00:54:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇做過aia 係咪伏</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好鬼忙.. 8點後收工是正常的...</blockquot