amp; customer services.<br />\n<br />\n其實aia做得唔錯.. 值得一試..</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n曾經無限接近過AIA group office 既intern 可惜最後無緣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n介唔介意講下點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\navailability <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都本來想過去做 Group 做個大project, 但無端端 Reject 咗.. 想Hea <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"091895eff1186442b0dd043e8e6eb6bd9aaeecab","tid":5732,"uid":47473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T04:05:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>畢業之後，做咗幾年嘢，都係喺保險公司工作..<br />\n做過GI, Life, Broker firm, 就係未做過Agent。接觸嘅工作範圍包括：Claim, UW, BD, Brokerage, AD, Distribution, IT, FP&amp;amp;A, Strategy, MIS..<br />\n<br />\n你哋問，我盡量答啦...<br />\n<br />\n利申：唔係Agent，無135牌</blockquote><br />\n做Local Broker, 專做GI, 無後生入行, 班老野無人接手迫賣盤</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係.. 我覺得班老嘢真係好廢，成個保險業俾佢哋搞到好唔專業..</blockquote><br />\n其實香港無咩正經途徑學保險，可以有幾專業"},{"pid":"183ca88797c8a42f38c396b56871c89a7fda3e75","tid":5732,"uid":26851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T05:09:45.000Z","msg":"巴打可唔可以分享入行過程同經歷 <br />\n<br />\nFg搵緊保險既back office 但係搵到既都係front line agent野 <br />\n<br />\n係香港講自己做保險好似過街老鼠咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1620f1fd55e8488bc22ab8f65455f6c0680cadae","tid":5732,"uid":47473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T05:28:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打可唔可以分享入行過程同經歷 <br />\n<br />\nFg搵緊保險既back office 但係搵到既都係front line agent野 <br />\n<br />\n係香港講自己做保險好似過街老鼠咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都唔係既，多數做商業客，成日大番個客轉頭"},{"pid":"d5f47a35e885401e616488f19d962830a8274b77","tid":5732,"uid":22148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T06:01:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打可唔可以分享入行過程同經歷 <br />\n<br />\nFg搵緊保險既back office 但係搵到既都係front line agent野 <br />\n<br />\n係香港講自己做保險好似過街老鼠咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n心態要正確囉！<br />\n<br />\n香港保險業已經被前線Agent搞到形象好差，我初初都唔慣。但慢慢做落，你會發現保險同銀行或者其他公司都好類近，有Distribution, UW, Claims, Operation, CS 和其他Function, IT, Finance and etc. <br />\n<br />\n相比銀行，保險公司形象的確麻麻，不過因為法理監管，保險公司一般都好穩陣，好少會大量炒人，亦唔會令個客血本無歸。保險產品保本能力強，回報算合理，而銀行就算有雷曼事件，都仲有正面形象，咪又係宣傳，加食水深。<br />\n<br />\n所以，入得保險公司，都係預咗穩定、特別專業係保險產品，要忍受咪一般人對保險的有色眼鏡。"},{"pid":"55dd39c7e1f54bff593ef6882d6e8fefee7a705c","tid":5732,"uid":22148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T06:05:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>畢業之後，做咗幾年嘢，都係喺保險公司工作..<br />\n做過GI, Life, Broker firm, 就係未做過Agent。接觸嘅工作範圍包括：Claim, UW, BD, Brokerage, AD, Distribution, IT, FP&amp;amp;amp;A, Strategy, MIS..<br />\n<br />\n你哋問，我盡量答啦...<br />\n<br />\n利申：唔係Agent，無135牌</blockquote><br />\n做Local Broker, 專做GI, 無後生入行, 班老野無人接手迫賣盤</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係.. 我覺得班老嘢真係好廢，成個保險業俾佢哋搞到好唔專業..</blockquote><br />\n其實香港無咩正經途徑學保險，可以有幾專業</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你可以讀 FLMI, Anziif, ACII<br />\n或者考精算試 SOA<br />\n<br />\n點會無？只是香港人個個走去讀BBA，想入Bank做，咪又係Sales!"},{"pid":"e09bdab20469526d6cc10aabb8617ea92185316a","tid":5732,"uid":22148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T06:06:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打可唔可以分享入行過程同經歷 <br />\n<br />\nFg搵緊保險既back office 但係搵到既都係front line agent野 <br />\n<br />\n係香港講自己做保險好似過街老鼠咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都唔係既，多數做商業客，成日大番個客轉頭</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打做 GI Broker?"},{"pid":"2a1e9e8ed53ac757b4bbabe97cd7a874c4682e10","tid":5732,"uid":2137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T06:08:56.000Z","msg":"宏利個醫保Plan 好定萬通個plan 好？另外，請教咩叫做&quot;自付額條款&quot;？"},{"pid":"2d4026c1bd870151b61013d052121176fd75180b","tid":5732,"uid":47473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T07:55:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>畢業之後，做咗幾年嘢，都係喺保險公司工作..<br />\n做過GI, Life, Broker firm, 就係未做過Agent。接觸嘅工作範圍包括：Claim, UW, BD, Brokerage, AD, Distribution, IT, FP&amp;amp;amp;A, Strategy, MIS..<br />\n<br />\n你哋問，我盡量答啦...<br />\n<br />\n利申：唔係Agent，無135牌</blockquote><br />\n做Local Broker, 專做GI, 無後生入行, 班老野無人接手迫賣盤</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係.. 我覺得班老嘢真係好廢，成個保險業俾佢哋搞到好唔專業..</blockquote><br />\n其實香港無咩正經途徑學保險，可以有幾專業</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你可以讀 FLMI, Anziif, ACII<br />\n或者考精算試 SOA<br />\n<br />\n點會無？只是香港人個個走去讀BBA，想入Bank做，咪又係Sales!</blockquote><br />\nAnziif 尾水Fellowship 拎左啦<br />\nPEAK 搞得差個course 摺左，後人無得係香港再報fellow. <br />\n得個弱鷄PDI<br />\n<br />\nLOMA 就考左一半，慢慢考，扣足5年CPD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nACII 就拎埋LOMA之後，搞prior learning，再扣CPD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43fb154cdd5879628fb29176e2cb8aebbc634541","tid":5732,"uid":47473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T07:57:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>畢業之後，做咗幾年嘢，都係喺保險公司工作..<br />\n做過GI, Life, Broker firm, 就係未做過Agent。接觸嘅工作範圍包括：Claim, UW, BD, Brokerage, AD, Distribution, IT, FP&amp;amp;amp;A, Strategy, MIS..<br />\n<br />\n你哋問，我盡量答啦...<br />\n<br />\n利申：唔係Agent，無135牌</blockquote><br />\n做Local Broker, 專做GI, 無後生入行, 班老野無人接手迫賣盤</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係.. 我覺得班老嘢真係好廢，成個保險業俾佢哋搞到好唔專業..</blockquote><br />\n其實香港無咩正經途徑學保險，可以有幾專業</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你可以讀 FLMI, Anziif, ACII<br />\n或者考精算試 SOA<br />\n<br />\n點會無？只是香港人個個走去讀BBA，想入Bank做，咪又係Sales!</blockquote><br />\nAnziif 尾水Fellowship 拎左啦<br />\nPEAK 搞得差個course 摺左，後人無得係香港再報fellow. <br />\n得個弱鷄PDI<br />\n<br />\nLOMA 就考左一半，慢慢考，扣足5年CPD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nACII 就拎埋LOMA之後，搞prior learning，再扣CPD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不過有幾多人讀，心照啦"},{"pid":"0411a1c42c360c807d5180e0715bbe8ce30f51cd","tid":5732,"uid":47473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T07:58:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打可唔可以分享入行過程同經歷 <br />\n<br />\nFg搵緊保險既back office 但係搵到既都係front line agent野 <br />\n<br />\n係香港講自己做保險好似過街老鼠咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都唔係既，多數做商業客，成日大番個客轉頭</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打做 GI Broker?</blockquote><br />\nGI LT Link MPF 都有，主要GI都夠"},{"pid":"bc7220427a96b715814d66b9ea5aaec8eb1df3d3","tid":5732,"uid":28594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T08:37:17.000Z","msg":"點睇manulife Corporate Management Trainee Program, 2017 August Intake (Back Office Non-Sales Position) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 應該有得1st round in<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4939c0a4de751a16c2793b95a13b002d9a5def61","tid":5732,"uid":19824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T11:11:27.000Z","msg":"有咩保險係值得買，唔會被人坤？<br />\n<br />\n利申： 啱啱出黎做野，由細到大未買過一份保險"},{"pid":"23e7a939ae697de47a6b4ac29621a2e0154e6ccc","tid":5732,"uid":6152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T11:21:58.000Z","msg":"啱啱開始做前線<br />\n講真上堂真係洗腦 加on9<br />\n希望自己可以做到清泉"},{"pid":"e4191c0515cbb8f805b64e9aa7494a21b202ff1d","tid":5732,"uid":6152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T11:26:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有咩保險係值得買，唔會被人坤？<br />\n<br />\n利申： 啱啱出黎做野，由細到大未買過一份保險</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打 我建議你花少少時間研究下<br />\n睇下有無需要 買自己合適既產品<br />\n可以既去compare埋<br />\n如果唔洗負擔屋企 可以買saving 有保障個d<br />\n如果可能有運動易病易受傷 咪買啲一般意外醫療<br />\n希望幫到你<br />\n<br />\n利申： 啱啱入行"},{"pid":"c582106b0fb43032778fadb5c38b5508d8d035a9","tid":5732,"uid":37954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T04:48:14.000Z","msg":"讀緊精算但係grad左唔太想做精算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果都係做保險公司巴打有冇咩建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58da40d082c077075988a86daab6a3b6a448be49","tid":5732,"uid":22148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T02:19:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>讀緊精算但係grad左唔太想做精算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果都係做保險公司巴打有冇咩建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做 data 囉.. 但請讀埋個master..<br />\n<br />\n唔係IT，係data science.. 但香港岩岩起步，唔太重視"},{"pid":"7fd25b7764a8d6b07d0b8516833eed30573dbc54","tid":5732,"uid":61631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T03:44:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大家冷靜d.. 唔好俾咁多負評.. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我哋唔係agent, 佢哋都係自己打自己工<br />\n<br />\n其實我哋都好怕d agents.. 佢哋為咗做生意無所不用其極<br />\n<br />\n而家香港得返2-3成係agent數，但佢哋d行為搞垮成個行業 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n得返2-3成agent數 你個間咩公司黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c14b298c4c24c92ffaff6341affa3b1110a3d515","tid":5732,"uid":69924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T23:34:11.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"d49116e2865cd73eba0fd732774742bb00c9b88d","tid":5732,"uid":30244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T00:31:00.000Z","msg":"想問下做EC有無前景？"},{"pid":"4e38ad9e0da590b6bb27cb432f8264e8196fe443","tid":5732,"uid":31744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T09:00:10.000Z","msg":"有邊種saving值得買？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔介意巴打開埋名"},{"pid":"f465f4a20bf7ccd8eceada30b6a5cb8a8a5d1efb","tid":5732,"uid":22148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T10:12:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問下做EC有無前景？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點為之前景先？<br />\n仲有你做邊Part先？Broker? UW? Claims?<br />\n仲有你做邊種Risk? 飲食？建築？定咩？<br />\n<br />\nEC: 俗稱 Employee Compensation, 主要係保障返員工工作時嘅保險產品。根據勞工條例，每個僱主必須為僱員顧買相關保險，自僱人士除外。產品範圍知識甚廣，不同行業，不同工種亦有不同Terms and Conditions!!! <br />\n<br />\n前景咪唔會餓死囉，好Steady咁Grow... 但 General Insurance 一般唔會有好 Outstanding performance.."},{"pid":"35ee26eeaad3117d9ce2c419ea57ee90b95caed0","tid":5732,"uid":6152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T15:54:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有邊種saving值得買？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔介意巴打開埋名</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打要穩穩陣陣 定投資成分高?"},{"pid":"e8e81044119f73f7317c86b2aa45314162c05990","tid":5732,"uid":47493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T16:09:15.000Z","msg":"巴打連IT都知？想問下salary大概係點？同埋其實主要做咩？寫program? Thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4880c348815b16bcbe72c7dfb685f1581c509cca","tid":5732,"uid":47493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T05:10:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打連IT都知？想問下salary大概係點？同埋其實主要做咩？寫program? Thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bea96c40e47be89c1d8640a1e3418ab1d75549d","tid":5732,"uid":69924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-05T00:04:28.000Z","msg":"萬用壽險對個客好唔好。唔係去到融資果種level"},{"pid":"5abaf7c1afc7862ff8500bee0d9b50d6d2b2db32","tid":5732,"uid":61249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-05T00:28:55.000Z","msg":"可唔可以講下 上面d broker claim 果d terms,  好多專業名詞睇唔明"},{"pid":"e4f97a34860b75d023c303163e81659a5b456e6d","tid":5732,"uid":7980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-05T00:51:54.000Z","msg":"Fg係間細公司學緊marine underwriting. 留名<br />\n巴打點睇？<br />\n仲諗緊好唔好訓身係呢行去考ACII"},{"pid":"00e